title: #50: Fifty Riddles GUARANTEED!
itunes:title: #50: Fifty Riddles GUARANTEED!
description:
How did we get here?! It's episode 50 and to celebrate we are doing fifty riddles in just over an hour. Some said it couldn't be done! Join us in this mad dash against time as some of our favorite characters, guests and collaborators pop on to wish us... well I don't know if they really wished us anything, but we have lots of fun surprises in store. Even if you never listen again, you're GOING TO WANT TO CHECK OUT THIS EP! #WiddleWednesday

Starring:

Adal Rifai

John Patrick Coan

Erin Keif

Editing by: 

KJ Snyder

Theme by: 

Arne Parrott

Logo by: 

Emily Kardamis & Emmaline Morris
